      "message": "This would leak the memory when the thread exits, but pthread_setspecific doesn’t really have any good reason to fail here.\n\nSince it doesn’t have any reason to fail, but failure would result in a hidden leak (well, OK, not entirely hidden, because there’s this LOG message, but the message doesn’t really convey the full severity of the problem), consider upgrading this to a PCHECK.",
